    <objectives>
      <material>
        <mattext texttype="text/html">&lt;h1&gt;Session 17 Quiz – Player and Hand Management&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Test your understanding of Player class, hand management, and score tracking.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Topics Covered:&lt;/strong&gt;
- Player class properties and methods
- Hand array manipulation
- Score tracking and updates
- Adding and removing cards
- Class method implementation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Instructions:&lt;/strong&gt;
- 16 questions from the Session 17 question bank
- 20 minute time limit
- 3 attempts allowed
- 16 points total (1 point per question)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;After syncing the question bank to Canvas:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</mattext>
      </material>
    </objectives>
